{"tid":1509221,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緊急！！！！！全世界同我入嚟。","createTime":"2019-08-26T18:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T01:03:29.000Z","uid":62011,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"92a5e33df43596f2f63581039e728b67afe0032d","tid":1509221,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T18:23:44.000Z","msg":"今日發生咗單野，泛民被葉劉代表發言話唔需要美國推行人權法。<br />\n<br />\n依家係關鍵時刻，建制賣港就一定，飯民會唔會賣港我唔知。但我唔想割席，亦都冇分裂本錢。<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋當自己係孤兒，冇人幫。呢刻我緊急呼籲各位採取以下行動<br />\n<br />\n1 自己去美議員媒體ACCT留言<br />\n［突發］立即去美國議員twitter展現民意！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1509113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1509113</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2 美國巴絲請入，請寫信畀當地議員<br />\n(國際線: 移居美國既巴絲請出手) - 一人一封遊說信比美國議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1495313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1495313</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n已經有TEMPLATE，請行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.  下次遊行集會，請大家舉牌，大字報寫 please pass HK human right and democracy act. 然後係外媒前揚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要救義士，關鍵時刻，大家要識做。"},{"pid":"f2220157f80f8bc87ba7e9341aef703844d6040b","tid":1509221,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T18:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=a83a2432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwit